consequences? Because I do.

34:13.291 --> 34:15.375
You know, I think about it.

34:17.375 --> 34:19.375
I'm just confused.

34:21.583 --> 34:23.291
What do you think
I should do?

34:25.542 --> 34:27.375
I can't tell you.

34:28.875 --> 34:32.125
Because you know.

34:32.125 --> 34:34.041
That's why we're friends.

34:35.375 --> 34:37.542
You know what's right for you
and do it.

34:37.542 --> 34:41.709
You don't care if it looks right
to other people or if it's safe.

34:41.709 --> 34:46.166
Well, that's what you need to do
now. And you know what?

34:47.417 --> 34:50.000
Everyone will survive.

34:51.500 --> 34:54.542
- Just do what you do.
- [groans]

34:56.375 --> 34:58.041
- Good morning.
