and I think we feel jealous
to see him...

35:30.375 --> 35:32.125
...loving someone else.

35:34.250 --> 35:36.959
I barely know the guy
so I have no excuse at all,

35:36.959 --> 35:40.917
except you're the hottest girl
here and my husband's the
hottest guy, so...

35:40.917 --> 35:43.667
I don't think your husband's
the hottest guy here.

35:43.667 --> 35:45.834
- Oh, you don't?
- No.

35:45.834 --> 35:48.917
Then, honey,
let's be best friends.

35:48.917 --> 35:51.291
- Who do you think
is the hottest guy?
- Yeah.

35:51.291 --> 35:53.792
- Can I be totally honest?
- Absolutely.

35:53.792 --> 35:56.417
- Dave.
- Oh, my God!

35:56.417 --> 35:59.917
- He's totally hot!
- I cannot wait to tell him!

35:59.917 --> 36:02.166
My God!
I'm having a girly conversation!

36:02.166 --> 36:04.583
Yes, you are!
And I love your earrings.

36:04.583 --> 36:06.166
- I love yours.
- Thank you.

36:08.542 --> 36:13.917
You know, Marjorie,
last night was fantastic.

36:15.875 --> 36:18.125
And it felt so familiar.

36:23.375 --> 36:25.041
But...?

36:31.208 --> 36:34.959
It's too late... for us.

36:40.709 --> 36:43.166
- I love you.
- [sobs]

36:45.458 --> 36:48.792
And a part of me
will always love you.

36:51.250 --> 36:53.417
But I can't erase the past.

36:57.250 --> 36:59.834
And I don't want
to start from there.

37:03.166 --> 37:04.917
I want to start fresh.

37:14.750 --> 37:16.834
