you want to say?

37:18.917 --> 37:20.834
I know that we
could be happy.

37:26.083 --> 37:28.750
I got scared
and I made a mistake.

37:32.959 --> 37:35.375
You know...

37:35.375 --> 37:39.792
...I believe that there
isn't just one person
out there to be happy with.

37:41.542 --> 37:43.709
You will find someone else.

37:49.041 --> 37:52.458
Maybe.

